# Walkthrough - Vehicle Data Implementation

## Changes
### LogiTrack Web App
#### [index.html](file:///c:/Users/tiesm/.gemini/antigravity/index.html)
- **Dump Registration Modal (`#add-truck-form`)**:
    - Added `TruckID` input field (auto-generated or manual).
    - Renamed "Capacity" to "積載容量 (m3)".
